{"tid":2009346,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"到底點先可以係屋企沖出港式凍奶茶？","createTime":"2020-05-09T16:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T17:35:13.000Z","uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a803f7c869fbc0d0c061ad9047985b2c6ec8ccf","tid":2009346,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"最近係屋企試下自己沖下港式飲品，但成品都唔理想<br />\n<br />\n以下係我個步驟：<br />\n首先係茶包浸熱水沖茶再加糖<br />\n茶包用過立頓、亦試過係超市買果啲所謂港式紅茶茶包<br />\n糖就普通白砂糖<br />\n然後拎走茶包搞勻 入雪櫃<br />\n雪凍後加淡奶飲，牌子係黑白牌<br />\n<br />\n結果入口好似午後紅茶之類果啲樽裝野既味道，完全唔係果回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又試過唔落淡奶落檸檬沖凍檸茶，啲味又係好撚奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以分享下港式飲品心得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c80a64000c961c6db02eacccc995b45b49158a","tid":2009346,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9IgjZBk5oNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9IgjZBk5oNk&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpRnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=18043ccd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9IgjZBk5oNk</a>"},{"pid":"e0b9d6c1e8e97bc57ba2bfe72b314f9f08c340ce","tid":2009346,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:28:17.000Z","msg":"茶餐廳用既茶膽<br />\n嘔到發霉咁滯<br />\n啖茶濃到仆街先沖得出個陣味<br />\n<br />\n你用十個茶包沖一杯應該都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf4f0b57fed97ce728c8262ab029cf222f91f9c","tid":2009346,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"去茶葉鋪同佢講要嚟煲奶茶佢會執俾你，要幾款茶葉溝埋先係果隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3